  m_Name: How do you get a girl to love you
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::DialogueSequence
  dialogueNodes:
  - Message:
      Message: Focusing on yourself is a great way to be more attractive to others.
        Try building up your personal skills.
      SpeakerTitle: Chad
    DialogueActionsStart: []
    DialogueActionsEnd: []
    Options: []
  - Message:
      Message: People want someone well-rounded, with several good qualities.
      SpeakerTitle: Chad
    DialogueActionsStart: []
    DialogueActionsEnd: []
    Options: []
  - Message:
      Message: Girls also like to feel heard. Listen to her likes and dislikes, and
        put in effort to show that you listened.
      SpeakerTitle: Chad
    DialogueActionsStart: []
    DialogueActionsEnd: []
    Options: []
  - Message:
      Message: 'You''ve got this, John Guy. '
      SpeakerTitle: Chad
